[26/05/2019 12:35:31] <font color="#ff00ff">y tenemos este paté tan rico.</font>
[26/05/2019 12:35:33] <font color="#ffff00">Casero.</font>
[26/05/2019 12:35:33] <font color="#ff00ff">Casero.</font>
[26/05/2019 12:35:34] <font color="#ff00ff">Y acompañamos</font>
[26/05/2019 12:35:34] <font color="#ff00ff">con unos pepinillos agridulces.</font>
