[26/05/2019 23:00:43] <font color="#ffff00">Así le damos una sorpresa.</font>
[26/05/2019 23:00:44] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[26/05/2019 23:00:44] <font color="#ffff00">¿Sí?</font>
[26/05/2019 23:01:29] <font color="#ffffff">(Claxon)</font>
[26/05/2019 23:01:33] <font color="#ffffff">"Bonne matinée".</font>
[26/05/2019 23:01:33] <font color="#00ff00">" a va?".</font>
